Package: linux-image-3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Provides: linux-image, linux-modules-3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64
Pre-Depends: debconf | debconf-2.0
Depends: kmod | module-init-tools (>= 3.16), ${misc:Depends}, initramfs-tools (>= 0.99~) [amd64] | linux-initramfs-tool [amd64]
Recommends: firmware-linux-free (>= 3~)
Suggests: linux-doc-3.3, crda [amd64], grub-pc [amd64] | extlinux [amd64] | grub-efi-amd64 [amd64]
Breaks: initramfs-tools (<< 0.99~)
Conflicts: r8168-dkms
Description: Linux 3.3 for 64-bit PCs
 The Linux kernel 3.3 and modules for use on PCs with AMD64 or Intel 64
 processors.

Package: linux-image-siduction-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Section: metapackages
Priority: extra
Depends: linux-image-3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: linux-headers-siduction-amd64 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Linux image for siduction on 64-bit PCs
 This metapackage depends on the latest binary image for Linux kernel on
 PCs with AMD64 or Intel 64 processors machines for siduction.

Package: linux-headers-siduction-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Section: metapackages
Priority: extra
Depends: linux-headers-3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux header for siduction on 64-bit PCs
 This metapackage depends on the latest binary image for Linux kernel on
 PCs with AMD64 or Intel 64 processors machines for siduction.

Package: linux-headers-3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Provides: linux-headers
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, gcc-4.6
Conflicts: r8168-dkm
Description: Header files for Linux 3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64
 This package provides the architecture-specific kernel header files for
 Linux kernel 3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64, generally used for building
 out-of-tree kernel modules.  These files are going to be installed into
 /usr/src/linux-headers-3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64, and can be used for
 building modules that load into the kernel provided by the
 linux-image-3.3-2.towo.1-siduction-amd64 package.

